{"tid":2422500,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"財政預算案後新港城3房賣818萬 高估價52萬","createTime":"2021-02-25T08:35:05.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-28T13:56:39.000Z","uid":73269,"like":4,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"4ab4a6b8dc20755a196083fe73984e58ecf12906","tid":2422500,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T08:35:05.000Z","msg":"[遲買更貴] 新一份財政預算案對樓市著墨不多，無礙買家入市信心，馬鞍山新港城一個3房減價以818萬元易手。美聯馬鞍山雲海分行首席高級營業經理黃家樂表示，新港城H座中層1室，實用面積519平方呎，3房間隔，以818萬元易手，實用呎價15,762元。<ins><strong><span class=\"red\">售價較估價766萬元高出52萬元</span></strong></ins>。<br />\n原業主於2012年以410萬元購入，持貨9年帳面獲利408萬元，單位升值約1倍。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"690a7a2d0b1ae8ba4e0ac88b6ea9e74eb2977c1a","tid":2422500,"uid":138809,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T09:09:08.000Z","msg":"519平方呎，3房<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03e3f28556d2dca2bd5945207be25be92704d471","tid":2422500,"uid":299123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T09:11:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />最近出左少左po喎"},{"pid":"edacfcc5231f668380dfeffc9b5de37f9a4e2596","tid":2422500,"uid":364041,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T09:46:50.000Z","msg":"收皮啦你傻閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54d7bf213825ccdd90a4e9ae3b8c2d55ba0de798","tid":2422500,"uid":357710,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"690a7a2d0b1ae8ba4e0ac